				<p>let me know if you want your website to be here (or a shoutout! cuz otherwise main page looks lonely...):</p>
				<ul>
					<li>your-website-could-be-here</li>
					<li>or-your-name!</li>
				</ul>
				<p>contact me: @_akuyu on both twitter and discord<br>do not hesitate to ask me anything you want, "i wont bite" as they say</p>
